(39, 1, '2014-10-20 16:50:45', '2014-10-20 13:50:45', '<a href="http://dev.dionworks.com/norm//wp-content/uploads/2014/10/norm-makine.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-48" src="http://dev.dionworks.com/norm//wp-content/uploads/2014/10/norm-makine.png" alt="norm-makine" width="470" height="342" /></a>Norm Makine is established to feel, understand and meet the needs of our clients in order to ease their lives. Our company is growing and progressing day by day with our flexible business approach and with the aim to be a part of the innovation aganist the competition for changing the world. Thus, we do our best to assist our clients to reach their goals. To continue the finest service to the clients, Norm Makine moved its headquarters to its 3000 m2 new built premises covering 2000 m2 showroom to exhibit from engine accessories to engines, from marine engine to open/closed type generators.\r\n\r\nDaewoo expand marine engines to every part of the world with USA, Far East and Europe being its primary export markets, is leading the market in Spain, Portugal, England, Italy, Norway and Greece. As a market leader in countries with expanded marine industry, Daewoo succeed to lead the top also in Turkish market through our company. Daewoo\'s in developing Turkish marine engine market, is not any different than its interest in any other developed country\'s marine sector. While drawing all clients\' attention in Turkey with its position engine, compact design and high durability, Daewoo consolidated its market position in Turkey with our company\'s technical support and profess,onal after sales services. Since our understanding in business, like Daewoo is to create the solid and the reliable, Turkish clients have realized not to content theirselves with what is offered. They demanded the best and gave us their hands. We, as Norm Makine, are working hard to grasp tightly every hand that reached us, without a step backwards. "NOT ENOUGH"\r\n\r\nNorm Makine distributes, DIESEL GENERATOR SETS with quality\'s approved and over the world high technology product engines which coupled with alternators, Norm Makine offers an excellent service which is relevant to your energy needs without any doubt. Considering what shall we accomplish, rather than what we have accomplished, we are saying that, a life built with the best, is an endless adventure. Who offers the best, will have the greatest share in this adventure. That means we are with you at every stop and every issue, "untill you complete your journey"... Being aware of that our company has organized a new marketing network with Dong-I and JMP, to develop permanent and instant solutions to the one of clients by providing marine engine components such as transmissions, pumps and seawater filters. Although those seem like performance components, lackage of these may lead to a discontinual of businesses, which means loosing of two essentials; time and money. That is why we began to sell engine components seperatly or as a complete set depening our client requirements. Our freezone warehouse and headquarters organised  according to the necessity of our at any moment. We are at your service all the time with our wide range products such as engines, engine accesories, marine generator, open / closed type generator warehouse and large spare part warehouses. This is "NOT ENOUGH", we will carry our success in marketing Daewoo, Dong-I and JMP products also to our after sales service activities in order to give complete and the best service to our clients.\r\n\r\nAs Norm Makine it\'s our promise to pay great attention to little details that we will create great step traces by our company\'s understanding principles and experiences... Until you complete your journey.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2014-11-26 12:49:42', '2014-11-26 10:49:42', '', 0, 'http://dev.dionworks.com/norm//?page_id=39', 7, 'page', '', 0),
