(583, 1, '2014-11-06 18:18:03', '2014-11-06 16:18:03', '<p align="justify"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">JMP electro magnetic clutch pumps are multi-purpose pumps widely used in agricultural, industrial and marine. Especially in marine uses you can used in high capacity bilge or deckwash and emergency fire fighting pumps. JMP clutch pumps have high quality and high performance with good price so you can use clutch pumps with full satisfaction of performance and price. Also you can easily replace the wearing parts and service kits are available.</span></p>\r\n<p align="left"><b><img src="http://www.norm.com.tr/urunler/electricfoto/ball02c.gif" alt="" width="16" height="10" /><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">High Power( High Torque ), High Capacity</span>\r\n<span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><img src="http://www.norm.com.tr/urunler/electricfoto/ball02c.gif" alt="" width="16" height="10" />Aluminum Pulley - Reduce Belt temperature\r\n<img src="http://www.norm.com.tr/urunler/electricfoto/ball02c.gif" alt="" width="16" height="10" />Easy to change the Pulley\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><img src="http://www.norm.com.tr/urunler/electricfoto/ball02c.gif" alt="" width="16" height="10" />Strong Bronze Body.\r\n<img src="http://www.norm.com.tr/urunler/electricfoto/ball02c.gif" alt="" width="16" height="10" />Full Rotation Pipe Work with rotating Impeller casing (M50, M65)\r\n</span><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><img src="http://www.norm.com.tr/urunler/electricfoto/ball02c.gif" alt="" width="16" height="10" />Spray Painting of clutch surface to be strong for rust.</span></b></p>\r\n<p align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">The clutch pumps give flow rates from 90 l/min up to 600 l/min(1" to 2 1/2")at 1800rpm.</span></p>', 'JRP-M25IP', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jrp-m25ip-2', '', '', '2015-01-13 15